dream: Basically I was like watching an episode of King of the hill. Not actually watching an episode but it felt like it. Like it basically wanted to lure me into a sense of comfort. But then it took me into a cave with one of the characters. And the character stopped being them and became me. There was a fridge in the cave full of meat and cheese and then someone came screaming and yelling not to eat any of it. Obv I didn't cuz if some disheveled freak comes at you you listen. They ran away and I never saw them again. I kept exploring the cave and there were like things trying to kill me. I wanna say they were people but it was really uncanny and they didn't feel like people. Also at this point I knew I was trapped in the cave forever because the cave kept changing like I'd turn around and it would have changed into something different. It's like I kind of knew I was dreaming but I couldn't wake up. Until eventually I made it back to the place with the fridge and there was this girl there. She was acting really mysterious but like in a playful way just teasing me. Eventually she tells me that she's in the same boat as me and the people keeping her down here just opened a door for her to meet me. Soon we meet a person sleeping in a room full of old gears and cogs. She wakes her up. It takes a long time for her to wake up tho. I find out that the girl I was with knows her. While they were talking I find out that she "works here" and maybe she can help us get out. But she doesn't take us anywhere. Soon I start putting all the cogs together on some kind of machine further into the cave hoping it'll lead to something. It doesn't do anything to get us out except turn on some kind of projection of the night sky. Me and the girl just sit there staring at it. Worried that we won't ever get out. That's when I wake up
interpretation:
In this dream, watching an episode of King of the Hill may symbolize a desire for comfort and familiarity. The cave represents a situation or state of mind that you feel trapped in. The character becoming you suggests a merging or identification with certain aspects of yourself. The fridge filled with food represents temptation and the warning not to eat it signifies caution and self-preservation.

The uncanny people trying to kill you can symbolize internal or external pressures that are threatening your sense of self. The changing nature of the cave reflects your awareness of being stuck in a repetitive or cyclical pattern, with the inability to fully escape or move forward.

Meeting the mysterious girl who is also trapped indicates a longing for connection and understanding in your current circumstances. The person sleeping in the room of gears and cogs can represent the potential for change or finding a solution. The projection of the night sky may represent hope or a longing for something beyond your current situation.

Overall, this dream suggests a feeling of being trapped in a difficult or uncertain situation. It reflects a mix of fear, longing for freedom, and the search for a way out. Consider exploring ways to break free from any limitations or constraints in your waking life.
